trans-unit.source: Represents a cell in the rendered table of a tabular ASP.NET data-bound control, such as <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView"></xref> or <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma célula da tabela renderizada de um controle de associação de dados tabular do ASP.NET, como <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView"> </xref> ou <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The DataControlFieldCell class is a strongly typed <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell> class that represents a cell in ASP.NET data-bound controls that render their contents in a tabular layout, such as <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView>.
trans-unit.target: A classe DataControlFieldCell é uma <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell>classe que representa uma célula em controles de associação de dados do ASP.NET que processar seu conteúdo em um layout tabular, como <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>e <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell> de fortemente tipada

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField> object that contains the DataControlFieldCell object controls how the cell is rendered by applying styles to the cell.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>objeto que contém o objeto DataControlFieldCell controla como a célula é renderizada aplicando estilos de célula.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>

trans-unit.source: You can access the containing <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField> object using the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell.ContainingField%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Você pode acessar o contendo <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>objeto usando o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell.ContainingField%2A>propriedade.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell.ContainingField%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell"></xref> class, setting the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"></xref> object as the cell's container.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell"> </xref> classe, definindo especificado <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"> </xref> objeto como contêiner da célula.

trans-unit.source: This constructor uses the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriterTag?displayProperty=fullName> element defined by its base class to render the cell.
trans-unit.target: Este construtor usa o <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriterTag?displayProperty=fullName>elemento definido por sua classe base para renderizar a célula.</xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriterTag?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField> object passed in the `containingField` parameter is used to determine whether to show headers and what styles to apply to the cell when it is rendered.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>objeto passado a `containingField` parâmetro é usado para determinar se deseja mostrar cabeçalhos e quais estilos para aplicar à célula quando ele for renderizado.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"></xref> that contains the current cell.
trans-unit.target: O <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"> </xref> que contém a célula atual.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell"></xref> class, setting the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"></xref> object as the cell's container.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell"> </xref> classe, definindo especificado <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"> </xref> objeto como contêiner da célula.

trans-unit.source: The `tagKey` parameter is passed to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebControl> base class constructor, and controls the HTML tag that is emitted by the control.
trans-unit.target: O `tagKey` parâmetro é passado para o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebControl>base do construtor de classe e marca de controles HTML que é emitida pelo controle.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebControl>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField> passed in the `containingField` parameter is used to determine whether to show headers and what styles to apply to the cell when it is rendered.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>passado a `containingField` parâmetro é usado para determinar se deseja mostrar cabeçalhos e quais estilos para aplicar à célula quando ele for renderizado.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriterTag"></xref> that specifies the HTML tag to render for the cell.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriterTag"> </xref> que especifica a marca HTML para renderizar para a célula.

trans-unit.source: The default tag used by the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell"></xref> class is <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriterTag"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: A marca padrão usada pelo <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell"> </xref> classe é <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriterTag"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"></xref> that contains the current cell.
trans-unit.target: O <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"> </xref> que contém a célula atual.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"></xref> object that contains the current cell.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"> </xref> objeto que contém a célula atual.

trans-unit.source: The content rendering for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell> object might be affected by the various <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField> properties of the containing field, such as <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField.ItemStyle%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField.ControlStyle%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField.ShowHeader%2A>.
trans-unit.target: O processamento de conteúdo para o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell>objeto pode ser afetado pelas várias <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>Propriedades do campo, como <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField.ItemStyle%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField.ControlStyle%2A>e <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField.ShowHeader%2A>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField.ShowHeader%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField.ControlStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField.ItemStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"></xref> that contains the current cell, or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>, if no <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"></xref> is passed to the class constructor.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"> </xref> que contém a célula atual, ou <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>, se nenhum <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"> </xref> é passado para o construtor da classe.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that specifies whether the control validates client input.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define um valor que especifica se o controle valida a entrada do cliente.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the control validates client input; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Se o controle valida a entrada do cliente; Caso contrário, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
